    <bioghist>
      <head>Biography/History</head>
      <p>Edwin L. Shelton was president of the Maryland Coal &#38; Coke Company in Virginia. He acquired the deed and its history through certain mineral interests.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection contains three items: one letter, one Vellum Deed, and the history of the tract of land going back to the late 1700s.</p>
